%N A241992 Decimal expansion of the limit when n -> infinity of the product Product_{k=1..2n+1} e^(-1/4)*(1 - 1/(k+1))^((1/2)*k*(k+1)*(-1)^k).
%H A241992 Jean-Paul Allouche, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11139-014-9604-5">A note on products involving zeta(3) and Catalan's constant</a>, The Ramanujan Journal, Vol. 37, No. 1 (2015), pp. 79-88; <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1305.6247">arXiv preprint</a>, arXiv:1305.6247v3 [math.NT], 2013-2014.
